{"tid":187000,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴打絲打去過New Zealand?","createTime":"2017-04-04T15:28:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-23T12:18:06.000Z","uid":103364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aaa63ee1e4fcc102ff494015ec61da9f798e8e6a","tid":187000,"uid":103364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T15:28:43.000Z","msg":"準備五月中去12日<br />\n而行程打算係<br />\nDay1~3 AucKland<br />\nDay4~5 Rotorua<br />\nDay6~7 Wellington<br />\nDay8~9 Christchurch<br />\nDay10~12 Queenstone<br />\n<br />\n其實最主要嘅係想問去過嘅巴絲覺得NZ邊樣最值得玩或者去?<br />\n<br />\n因為以上而所講嘅係我好想去嘅城市 但另一方面又好去搭所謂世界上最靚嘅觀光火車由Christchurh到Greymounth附近行冰川 <br />\n 真係唔知點揀好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nThanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c77fba448d45b243d98a5a19ccbc32fb51543ab","tid":187000,"uid":43964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T15:38:30.000Z","msg":"悶到仆街，啲人幾友善"},{"pid":"a39e9884340ec355b1fad0c9f28c280a4cecbf9f","tid":187000,"uid":43361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T15:40:44.000Z","msg":"主力queenstown+ 睇冰川+ 風景 數羊"},{"pid":"abf34795277aad378554e30e2056bb28e0e49105","tid":187000,"uid":103364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T15:41:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>悶到仆街，啲人幾友善</blockquote><br />\n竟然 點解嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇資料又多活動景又靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a09b3760a426b1a8ca2dfef652da0ce538d5ffd6","tid":187000,"uid":33762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T15:43:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>準備五月中去12日<br />\n而行程打算係<br />\nDay1~3 AucKland<br />\nDay4~5 Rotorua<br />\nDay6~7 Wellington<br />\nDay8~9 Christchurch<br />\nDay10~12 Queenstone<br />\n<br />\n其實最主要嘅係想問去過嘅巴絲覺得NZ邊樣最值得玩或者去?<br />\n<br />\n因為以上而所講嘅係我好想去嘅城市 但另一方面又好去搭所謂世界上最靚嘅觀光火車由Christchurh到Greymounth附近行冰川 <br />\n 真係唔知點揀好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nThanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n只係去過北島，Auckland 無咩好玩，我覺得 waitomo caves ， Rotorua 一定要去"},{"pid":"960985479bb4ae628194cc9104121bb8a5afc8cc","tid":187000,"uid":34901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T16:02:04.000Z","msg":"應該留一晚去lake tekapo 睇星超靚"},{"pid":"e0c7bb9586e8bf18cde7c122422470e23308f8a0","tid":187000,"uid":59082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T16:04:12.000Z","msg":"我都係5月中去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n留個名先"},{"pid":"4881d4b4a046d746460e1abfe1cf7d1b8e545462","tid":187000,"uid":20811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T16:07:58.000Z","msg":"Auckland 我去casino 無乜野玩好似係，去過queens town  我可以玩好耐好耐如果再去的話！勁多野可以試，不過洗費好高（可能我是窮撚）好多戶外活動。但上次去冬天就凍到仆街"},{"pid":"f05c3c027278e464d76c40929b81e9add2b1e34e","tid":187000,"uid":103364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T02:40:09.000Z","msg":"其實威靈頓會唔會好悶 我係見佢首都先想去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"699d8741621ed2b461445af45dcc13ddc680d927","tid":187000,"uid":103364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T09:38:09.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc1af4eed11c893f15090d63b0c9b296a8e06b14","tid":187000,"uid":76632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T10:22:50.000Z","msg":"魔戒取景<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77ba06474811dcc888888833556fff43bfbde570","tid":187000,"uid":13257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T11:51:54.000Z","msg":"南島靚好多喎，花多d時間南島啦"},{"pid":"6c343b2c39a622d72ad85fe373812daad334a31e","tid":187000,"uid":97234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T11:58:02.000Z","msg":"去queens town 要跳傘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"956b5118519c317db631b7a867a9326ae125fee6","tid":187000,"uid":103232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T11:58:25.000Z","msg":"住過AKL兩年<br />\n可能我本身份人鐘意生活節奏慢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以AKL幾岩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然星期日CBD好多地方都唔開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f0c0e8f5a913764b3609a44772dcfe92d54399d","tid":187000,"uid":1333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T11:59:43.000Z","msg":"冰川風景係重點<br />\n未必個個岩玩<br />\n去行兩三個鐘山一流"},{"pid":"83bec594e7542602013ef1652f5d02a78230f4d4","tid":187000,"uid":4789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T13:40:30.000Z","msg":"去過七日北島，可以試下參加果啲full day tour,包門票午餐穿梭巴士，朝七至晚七 送翻你去auckland<br />\n<br />\n果陣我參加左兩個full day tour, 一個去hobbiton 加幾個cave. 另一個去rotorua.lee 個我就無跟車翻，係rotorua 落車。<br />\n<br />\n強烈建議參加rotorua 個tamaki maori village,真係好正！夜晚參加，又有自助餐食<br />\n<br />\n有需要我再post 個網出黎，好多tour 特價優惠，平到笑"},{"pid":"75be9b6ae5d1ab54ac89b4960bfc3dce882c276e","tid":187000,"uid":50554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T15:46:55.000Z","msg":"有車牌既租架露營車啦 係啲深山既營地過夜睇星正到不得了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63bb11cfd53a18f5206367d1f92731c71ab93949","tid":187000,"uid":103364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T04:44:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>住過AKL兩年<br />\n可能我本身份人鐘意生活節奏慢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以AKL幾岩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然星期日CBD好多地方都唔開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打點申請visa係akl住嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddd1b353dc0d97533679f093e04d68524b78ac76","tid":187000,"uid":103364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T04:45:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去過七日北島，可以試下參加果啲full day tour,包門票午餐穿梭巴士，朝七至晚七 送翻你去auckland<br />\n<br />\n果陣我參加左兩個full day tour, 一個去hobbiton 加幾個cave. 另一個去rotorua.lee 個我就無跟車翻，係rotorua 落車。<br />\n<br />\n強烈建議參加rotorua 個tamaki maori village,真係好正！夜晚參加，又有自助餐食<br />\n<br />\n有需要我再post 個網出黎，好多tour 特價優惠，平到笑</blockquote><br />\ntamaki maori village我都一定會去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但其他tour full day嘅話一般都要1000hkd 好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acf364c09a2d5ea603b01ba57ba60e7791a97423","tid":187000,"uid":39845,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T04:58:05.000Z","msg":"認真 紐西蘭最靚既風景係人<br />\nBtw藍光螢火蟲唔錯<br />\n其他唔記得 五六年前去"},{"pid":"1a132bb924610778ba83d2bab3c909be06136627","tid":187000,"uid":4789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T05:36:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>去過七日北島，可以試下參加果啲full day tour,包門票午餐穿梭巴士，朝七至晚七 送翻你去auckland<br />\n<br />\n果陣我參加左兩個full day tour, 一個去hobbiton 加幾個cave. 另一個去rotorua.lee 個我就無跟車翻，係rotorua 落車。<br />\n<br />\n強烈建議參加rotorua 個tamaki maori village,真係好正！夜晚參加，又有自助餐食<br />\n<br />\n有需要我再post 個網出黎，好多tour 特價優惠，平到笑</blockquote><br />\ntamaki maori village我都一定會去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但其他tour full day嘅話一般都要1000hkd 好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但你睇翻各個景點嘅入場票價，加埋仲貴過一千，仲要唔包交通，rotorua 果邊最煩係交通<br />\n另外可以去下taupo,好多野玩，但我之前因爲唔知,所以無預時間去<br />\n如果夠膽又有做開運動可以玩下lost world tour &amp; black water rafting。當然樣樣都係錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"995312520339e9b24bfca6425232d608a3907a05","tid":187000,"uid":33674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T05:44:46.000Z","msg":"留明<br />\n掙扎緊去邊個city 好，auckland 網上話冇乜好玩，定係去威靈頓+ Queenstown好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8dc6f20d8999a0b08d65b5a7e136ac4049bc712","tid":187000,"uid":4789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T06:01:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留明<br />\n掙扎緊去邊個city 好，auckland 網上話冇乜好玩，定係去威靈頓+ Queenstown好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n時間多又有預算就南北島去曬，先auckland再queenstown"},{"pid":"629e425ddb0171b612b68990f87e956e89d9b547","tid":187000,"uid":98891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T06:28:05.000Z","msg":"北島就去hobbiton, waitomo cave玩black water rafting, coromandel hot water beach+Cathedral cave, tongariro 行火山，rotorua Polynesia spa+睇下毛利文化"},{"pid":"9f9034a3d174aec6a2dac8ed969f604db59ef75a","tid":187000,"uid":33674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T07:00:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>留明<br />\n掙扎緊去邊個city 好，auckland 網上話冇乜好玩，定係去威靈頓+ Queenstown好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n時間多又有預算就南北島去曬，先auckland再queenstown</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n大約一星期，應該冇乜可能食晒兩家<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc13dd39362a924afb834a08fa0cdffbb586c363","tid":187000,"uid":77803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T07:02:48.000Z","msg":"都係5月中去，不過淨去南島<br />\nQueenstown入Christchurch 出<br />\n咩都未訂未plan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d2bdec409ce5a3d91b5897cf046167b31163c7a","tid":187000,"uid":2860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T07:10:22.000Z","msg":"去過16日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af24e9a4ca1a808745fca2691ba8ed51daae44b9","tid":187000,"uid":98349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T07:14:04.000Z","msg":"去過10日南島 自駕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65e750d4186408aac43f746c96a27988bc408b07","tid":187000,"uid":4789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T07:36:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>都係5月中去，不過淨去南島<br />\nQueenstown入Christchurch 出<br />\n咩都未訂未plan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果可以等七月大冬天先去，mount cook 積雪量夠，正"},{"pid":"79461ce7c0802b6cb4a7b1bb5d9ff5fc0a3f2a41","tid":187000,"uid":91317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T07:42:22.000Z","msg":"上年十月去完，淨係南島，我覺得全個旅程最正係milford sound 坐船兩日一夜，仙景一樣！"},{"pid":"54aad9fa0bb5e74d7845a9336aba91a1f13aff26","tid":187000,"uid":103998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T07:58:07.000Z","msg":"Auckland 幾悶，可以行上mount ed 頂睇晒成個auckland，建議黃昏去就最正，亦都可以搭船去隔離個waiheke 島，有好多葡萄酒莊，可以試下酒食下野，亦都有水上活動玩。<br />\n<br />\n由auckland去rotorua可以順便上intercity 報hobbiton連waitomo cave tour，一日睇完可以送埋你去旅館門口。rotorua 除左去village亦都可以行redwood（提外話，海旁有間all Day breakfast 好好食）<br />\n<br />\nWellington 一定要去佢個national museum. 可以行幾個鐘，都幾得意。亦可以行下cuba street，同埋一定要去飲下咖啡，聽講flat white 就係果到出黎架。<br />\n<br />\n講住咁多先。"},{"pid":"3cc7a84d7959c96cd7c4f36a5585f34f7c9f32e8","tid":187000,"uid":103364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T09:49:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Auckland 幾悶，可以行上mount ed 頂睇晒成個auckland，建議黃昏去就最正，亦都可以搭船去隔離個waiheke 島，有好多葡萄酒莊，可以試下酒食下野，亦都有水上活動玩。<br />\n<br />\n由auckland去rotorua可以順便上intercity 報hobbiton連waitomo cave tour，一日睇完可以送埋你去旅館門口。rotorua 除左去village亦都可以行redwood（提外話，海旁有間all Day breakfast 好好食）<br />\n<br />\nWellington 一定要去佢個national museum. 可以行幾個鐘，都幾得意。亦可以行下cuba street，同埋一定要去飲下咖啡，聽講flat white 就係果到出黎架。<br />\n<br />\n講住咁多先。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個個都話auckland悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇黎去玩一日就夠<br />\n<br />\n可唔可以講埋南島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee1b985c67dd5a0c1b6f1238341aa7ad4f284034","tid":187000,"uid":17386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T09:52:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去過七日北島，可以試下參加果啲full day tour,包門票午餐穿梭巴士，朝七至晚七 送翻你去auckland<br />\n<br />\n果陣我參加左兩個full day tour, 一個去hobbiton 加幾個cave. 另一個去rotorua.lee 個我就無跟車翻，係rotorua 落車。<br />\n<br />\n強烈建議參加rotorua 個tamaki maori village,真係好正！夜晚參加，又有自助餐食<br />\n<br />\n有需要我再post 個網出黎，好多tour 特價優惠，平到笑</blockquote><br />\n巴打可唔可以麻煩你post個網出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fccf06c1cbaf71ac3f787d08638eaaf81c6f4e22","tid":187000,"uid":52975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T09:53:28.000Z","msg":"Black water rafting 好正<br />\n螢火蟲靚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nPolynesian spa 一路睇星 一路浸溫泉"},{"pid":"9a632fde1197287c2d49fd86e37ef33be91a98bf","tid":187000,"uid":1307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T09:58:04.000Z","msg":"12日又玩北又玩南會好趕<br />\n我個陣10月去行山勁舒服 仲有少少雪係山頂"},{"pid":"7e519381376662ecdefd37f7cff760c58543f7c2","tid":187000,"uid":4789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T10:00:16.000Z","msg":"Auckland 可以去davenport 行下，食fish and chips 。黃昏睇日落可以去mission bay ，隔離有間雪糕店，食住雪糕行沙灘睇日落。。毒撚就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  利申 毒撚，不過家姐住nz 有人陪<br />\n玩就真係無野玩，不過我勝在散心，坐係座山上面坐左成個鐘發呆，諗下野，放鬆心情。一來景色好，二來空氣清新"},{"pid":"4f123ed69a9374d777d345a096ea9e14ab90cf42","tid":187000,"uid":37730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T10:00:30.000Z","msg":"基督城你留到咁耐？<br />\n<br />\n附近得Akaora叫好d<br />\n反而中間抽一日去kaikoura睇下鯨魚<br />\n或去lake tekapu 睇星更好"},{"pid":"d99125939fc3679d9c584bbc71613cba0b8f0f6b","tid":187000,"uid":37730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T10:03:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實威靈頓會唔會好悶 我係見佢首都先想去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我寫包單你會後悔"},{"pid":"8408653450e2d94cb599ac66d8776a3e88af419f","tid":187000,"uid":103364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T10:03:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>基督城你留到咁耐？<br />\n<br />\n附近得Akaora叫好d<br />\n反而中間抽一日去kaikoura睇下鯨魚<br />\n或去lake tekapu 睇星更好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n又好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n會再諗下 睇星都好吸引<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa3f68ab578f29d6154468bbdadfca841ab4cbf8","tid":187000,"uid":1307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T10:03:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>基督城你留到咁耐？<br />\n<br />\n附近得Akaora叫好d<br />\n反而中間抽一日去kaikoura睇下鯨魚<br />\n或去lake tekapu 睇星更好</blockquote><br />\nLake Tekapo 睇星好 我上次去左一日咁岩撞正多雲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nMt. Cook行山勁舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1740b61866169a1dd4ec7a7279dc2cc62764770","tid":187000,"uid":103364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T10:07:03.000Z","msg":"同埋想問下各位係nz自己行山會唔會好危險? 定係多數會跟團?"},{"pid":"8d3835203dee95a7c93dc7adb28b6d3ab3492d58","tid":187000,"uid":4789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T10:08:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>去過七日北島，可以試下參加果啲full day tour,包門票午餐穿梭巴士，朝七至晚七 送翻你去auckland<br />\n<br />\n果陣我參加左兩個full day tour, 一個去hobbiton 加幾個cave. 另一個去rotorua.lee 個我就無跟車翻，係rotorua 落車。<br />\n<br />\n強烈建議參加rotorua 個tamaki maori village,真係好正！夜晚參加，又有自助餐食<br />\n<br />\n有需要我再post 個網出黎，好多tour 特價優惠，平到笑</blockquote><br />\n巴打可唔可以麻煩你post個網出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個網叫bookme ,入面有好多tour ，睇清楚邊個啱自己，選日子果到紅色代表最平，橙色第二，黃色第三，白色原價"},{"pid":"7e9bd049d385c025da96ecfc8d5cfb552ef078d9","tid":187000,"uid":1307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T10:22:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同埋想問下各位係nz自己行山會唔會好危險? 定係多數會跟團?</blockquote><br />\n我個時其實幾大膽 靠個google map沿山路行行左大半日<br />\n沿途見到人上落既打聲招呼 講下路程要行幾耐咁確定自己位置係邊<br />\n要衡量自己體能 帶D野食(EG.麵包 能量棒)同水 計定來回時間同確保入黑前落到山<br />\n如果見到有人同樣目的地既可以問下對方介唔介意一齊行<br />\n小心為上 唔好蕩失路 唔好行小路"},{"pid":"646bc5138d7da65468a5fde2e00d14f566cf919c","tid":187000,"uid":103364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T10:29:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同埋想問下各位係nz自己行山會唔會好危險? 定係多數會跟團?</blockquote><br />\n我個時其實幾大膽 靠個google map沿山路行行左大半日<br />\n沿途見到人上落既打聲招呼 講下路程要行幾耐咁確定自己位置係邊<br />\n要衡量自己體能 帶D野食(EG.麵包 能量棒)同水 計定來回時間同確保入黑前落到山<br />\n如果見到有人同樣目的地既可以問下對方介唔介意一齊行<br />\n小心為上 唔好蕩失路 唔好行小路</blockquote><br />\n 巴打當時係行邊度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0078e664d0da0f6fd0bfb7d7d4d3936f366be1eb","tid":187000,"uid":1307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T10:48:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>同埋想問下各位係nz自己行山會唔會好危險? 定係多數會跟團?</blockquote><br />\n我個時其實幾大膽 靠個google map沿山路行行左大半日<br />\n沿途見到人上落既打聲招呼 講下路程要行幾耐咁確定自己位置係邊<br />\n要衡量自己體能 帶D野食(EG.麵包 能量棒)同水 計定來回時間同確保入黑前落到山<br />\n如果見到有人同樣目的地既可以問下對方介唔介意一齊行<br />\n小心為上 唔好蕩失路 唔好行小路</blockquote><br />\n 巴打當時係行邊度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nMt. Cook-Hooker Valley Track (行左去Mueller Lake &amp; Hooker Lake)<br />\nQueenstown-Queenstown Hill &amp; Ben Lomond (Ben Lomond 有一定難度)"},{"pid":"5b7e0206fa4232d367b8a3104781a9be091a3dc9","tid":187000,"uid":6817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T11:01:03.000Z","msg":"有冇機會睇到極光？"},{"pid":"dba849d5fdf675034a2d3e9a396a7cb703e13e07","tid":187000,"uid":56998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T11:02:03.000Z","msg":"信我<br />\nwaitomo black water rafting一定唔會後悔"},{"pid":"f0384c30f9e31eb1d7728fa8b5f3dcfd3230ef07","tid":187000,"uid":1307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T11:05:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>同埋想問下各位係nz自己行山會唔會好危險? 定係多數會跟團?</blockquote><br />\n我個時其實幾大膽 靠個google map沿山路行行左大半日<br />\n沿途見到人上落既打聲招呼 講下路程要行幾耐咁確定自己位置係邊<br />\n要衡量自己體能 帶D野食(EG.麵包 能量棒)同水 計定來回時間同確保入黑前落到山<br />\n如果見到有人同樣目的地既可以問下對方介唔介意一齊行<br />\n小心為上 唔好蕩失路 唔好行小路</blockquote><br />\n 巴打當時係行邊度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nMt. Cook-Hooker Valley Track (行左去Mueller Lake &amp; Hooker Lake)<br />\nQueenstown-Queenstown Hill &amp; Ben Lomond (Ben Lomond 有一定難度)</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.doc.govt.nz/aoraki-walking-tracks\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.doc.govt.nz%2Faoraki-walking-tracks&d=CEXeqV9R6719hdRRqmVjOkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=cc09e2ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.doc.govt.nz/aoraki-walking-tracks</a><br />\n依個網有埋預計行程成間 你可以有個概念黎搵個合適自己既行程"},{"pid":"b78eed8dd1231691d50e9148888df7d7c55b3772","tid":187000,"uid":1307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T11:06:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>同埋想問下各位係nz自己行山會唔會好危險? 定係多數會跟團?</blockquote><br />\n我個時其實幾大膽 靠個google map沿山路行行左大半日<br />\n沿途見到人上落既打聲招呼 講下路程要行幾耐咁確定自己位置係邊<br />\n要衡量自己體能 帶D野食(EG.麵包 能量棒)同水 計定來回時間同確保入黑前落到山<br />\n如果見到有人同樣目的地既可以問下對方介唔介意一齊行<br />\n小心為上 唔好蕩失路 唔好行小路</blockquote><br />\n 巴打當時係行邊度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nMt. Cook-Hooker Valley Track (行左去Mueller Lake &amp; Hooker Lake)<br />\nQueenstown-Queenstown Hill &amp; Ben Lomond (Ben Lomond 有一定難度)</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.doc.govt.nz/aoraki-walking-tracks\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.doc.govt.nz%2Faoraki-walking-tracks&d=CEXeqV9R6719hdRRqmVjOkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=cc09e2ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.doc.govt.nz/aoraki-walking-tracks</a><br />\n依個網有埋預計行程成間 你可以有個概念黎搵個合適自己既行程</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.doc.govt.nz/aoraki-walking-tracks\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.doc.govt.nz%2Faoraki-walking-tracks&d=CEXeqV9R6719hdRRqmVjOkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=cc09e2ea\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.doc.govt.nz/aoraki-walking-tracks</a>"},{"pid":"ed55d7de82cb1b24555d262e1fef169d7cc8fb3d","tid":187000,"uid":4789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T11:12:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>信我<br />\nwaitomo black water rafting一定唔會後悔</blockquote><br />\n無膽鬼表示好想參加，但真係好淆，又無運動怕做負累...<br />\n最想參加lee個，個view 好正<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/06/191208_45363e3dd26540b56e3aefde50c2f728.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F06%2F191208_45363e3dd26540b56e3aefde50c2f728.jpg&h=f12a0609&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}